ses below are included in Sequence Wiz database and can be used to design your unique yoga practices.";i:20;s:74:"Sequence Wiz members will get this infographic as a pdf handout on Friday.";i:21;s:169:"This Sun Salutations Chair Yoga Lesson Plan created using the Yoga Genie Lesson Planner is suitable for office workers seniors coach-potatoes and any one who loves yoga.";i:22;s:118:"There are 15 chair poses in the lesson plan following as closely as possible the traditional Sun Salutations sequence.";i:23;s:27:"Chair yoga for seniors pdf.";i:24;s:109:"Modified for the chair stronger seniors yoga chair exercise program incorporates all of the benefits of yoga.";i:25;s:72:"Chair yoga poses integrate the best of flexibility and balance training.";i:26;s:34:"You can do em right in your chair.";i:27;s:69:"In the last decade yoga for seniors has become more and more popular.";i:28;s:155:"Chair yoga sequences can also be done while working in front of the computer to give the body a gentle massage and stretch if one is seated for long hours.";i:29;s:70:"So chair yoga sequences are also beneficial for people with desk jobs.";i:30;s:108:"Please click on the sequence title to view the complete chair yoga sequence with detailed overview and cues.";i:31;s:253:"Chair yoga falls under the category of hatha yoga a form of yoga that uses breathing postures and meditation and is practiced while sitting in a chair standing and using the chair for support or a combination of both seated and supported standing poses.";i:32;s:132:"A chair practice incorporates all the tools of a regular asana class such as deep breathing poses and relaxation so you receive the.";i:33;s:102:"Chair Yoga Poses The following 10 poses are done one after another in the sequence they are presented.";i:34;s:90:"Begin by sitting in a chair with your spine very straight and your feet flat on the floor.";i:35;s:76:"Slowly inhale and arch your back while dropping your shoulders cow position.";i:36;s:40:"Slowly exhal