obility issues or struggle with balance anyone can do chair yoga and its especially great.";i:57;s:112:"Gentle Yoga Sequence for Emotional Well-Being Here is a set of yoga poses to support your yoga practice at home.";i:58;s:105:"It is recommended that you learn these poses with a trained yoga teacher before you try them on your own.";i:59;s:107:"Start by doing one or two poses a day and also think about adding little bits of yoga into your daily life.";i:60;s:160:"This sequence from Mindful Chair Yoga Deck by Jennifer Cohen Harper and Mayuri Gonzales can be done from almost anywhere and is appropriate for kids and adults.";i:61;s:18:"Get the book here.";i:62;s:75:"An Accessible Yoga Practice You Can Do In a Chair Belly Breath Carlos Bido.";i:63;s:66:"Sit tall with your feet on the floor and your hands on your belly.";i:64;s:24:"This is Seated Mountain.";}}